summary:
Peter Parker/Spider-Man and Felicia Hardy/Black Cat in Raise a Little Hell 
“ Regardless, she was still the same old Felicia...
body:
Peter Parker/Spider-Man and Felicia Hardy/Black Cat in Raise a Little Hell

“ Regardless, she was still the same old Felicia Hardy. The same girl that would run along side him and Ned, chasing butterflies on the grass field across the red and blue playground that the rest of their classmates played on. The same girl that would threaten anyone who picked on Peter or Ned for whatever superhero was on their lunch box or how far behind they were in PE. The same girl who never understood Star Wars but still tried to because her best friends loved that movie. The same girl that hated the other girls in their classes because all they wanted to make fun of Peter and Ned. The same girl that Peter had called his best friend way back when. Felicia Hardy, he knew that name, it was familiar to him, safe, home. “
